                                                <p><strong><u>Club Name</u>: </strong>&#160;California Land Surveyors Association</p>
<p><strong><u>Adviser(s)</u>:</strong> Omar Mora, Ph.D., L.S.I.T.</p>
<p>&#160;<img alt="" class="" height="281" src="../img/logo_clsa.jpg" width="298"/></p>

