                                                The Beavers Heavy Construction is offering an opportunity to continuing juniors and seniors in the College of Engineering whose major is in Construction Engineering and intend to pursue a career in heavy construction. <br/><br/>*Selection Criteria:*<br/> # Open to class levels: Junior and Senior (First-time transfer are encouraged to apply) <br/> # Major must be Construction Engineering <br/> # Must have a minimum cumulative GPA of 3.0 or higher<br/> # Demonstrate financial need by completing the FAFSA for 2020-2021<br/> # Submit a 200 word or less statement demonstrating your interest in a career in heavy construction <br/> # California residency is required

