                            <div aria-labelledby="heading1" class="collapse " data-parent="#accordion-14" id="collapse14-1">
                          <div class="card-body">










                                                <p>The&#160;Railway Association of Southern California (RASC) Board is committed to supporting students seeking careers in the rail transportation industry. This scholarship program is offered once a year to local students in the Southern California Region.&#160;This year RASC will be awarding two $3000 scholarships to undergraduate students and three $3000 scholarships to graduate students for a total of five.</p>
<p>The scholarships are competitive and are based on the applicant's specific involvement in transportation, career goals, and academic record. Please visit below for more information and application process:</p>
<p><a href="https://www.railwayassociation.org/scholarship">https://www.railwayassociation.org/scholarship</a></p>

